268
00:23:00,410 --> 00:23:01,420
You...

269
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:05,420
coming all this way to see me.

270
00:23:39,050 --> 00:23:40,050
Daniel!

271
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,800
