281
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:35,980
Yes.

282
00:24:38,410 --> 00:24:39,410
I'm his mother.

283
00:24:45,990 --> 00:24:46,990
Let me see.

284
00:25:01,870 --> 00:25:02,870
I'm sorry.

285
00:25:06,540 --> 00:25:08,910
For saying you're my mom?

286
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:12,880
No.

287
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,150
For not asking if you were okay,

288
00:25:20,890 --> 00:25:23,690
