311
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,470
Why "Oscar"?

312
00:27:47,570 --> 00:27:48,570
The name of the fish.

313
00:27:54,010 --> 00:27:55,010
Do you...

314
00:27:57,110 --> 00:27:58,980
