- And just sit there clapping.

352
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:44,610
- I can't sing...
- Hurry up and pick a song. Come on.

353
00:30:44,710 --> 00:30:47,110
- I'll sing.
- Yes!

354
00:30:47,450 --> 00:30:48,450
Goodness.

355
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,280
("Love Battery")

356
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:55,420
All right!

357
00:30:55,490 --> 00:30:58,260
Fill me up with your love

358
00:30:58,330 --> 00:30:59,330
Fill me up!

359
00:30:59,390 --> 00:31:02,630
I think my love battery has run out

360
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:06,900
I can't live without you, I really can't live

361
00:31:07,100 --> 00:31:09,440
You are my battery

362
00:31:09,500 --> 00:31:10,500
- Battery!
- Battery!

363
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:17,610
- You enjoyed today, Ja Yeong.
- I did.

364
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:21,280
I know. Who would've thought that one trip together...

365
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:24,420
