00:42:38,890 --> 00:42:39,930
Bean paste...

510
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:46,500
Oh, my! Raphael!

511
00:42:51,140 --> 00:42:52,140
Hello.

512
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:57,740
- Father, fancy seeing you here.
- It is, isn't it?

513
00:42:58,010 --> 00:43:01,480
We're with the Father to give communion to a new member.

514
00:43:01,510 --> 00:43:03,750
- I see.
- Raphael, how have you been?

515
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:07,690
Yes, I've been doing well, thanks to your prayers.

516
00:43:08,250 --> 00:43:10,090
You're looking so well.

517
00:43:10,990 --> 00:43:13,060
You seem much more at peace.

518
00:43:13,730 --> 00:43:14,830
I am, thank you.

519
00:43:16,160 --> 00:43:19,100
But I've heard it's not always that simple.

520
00:43:19,600 --> 00:43:22,970
The first year after losing a spouse is a critical time.

521
00:43:23,370 --> 00:43:24,800
You still need to finish your shopping.

522
00:43:24,870 --> 00:43:27,670
It's just that I'm so worried about you, Raphael.

523
00:43:30,140 --> 00:43:32,780
Oh, my, Father! Look who's with Raphael...

524
00:43:32,850 --> 00:43:34,910
Jin Ho. This should be enough, right?

525
00:43:37,450 --> 00:43:38,520
And you are?

526
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:46,690
This is...

527
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:49,360
